ostgreSQL 是一个强大的开源关系型数据库，通过丰富的插件生态可以覆盖多种数据场景。","content/6.maps/_database/postgres/index.md",{"type":183,"children":184,"toc":227},"root",[185,193,200,206,211],{"type":186,"tag":187,"props":188,"children":190},"element","h2",{"id":189},"扩展生态",[191],{"type":192,"value":189},"text",{"type":186,"tag":194,"props":195,"children":197},"h4",{"id":196},"postgres-能替代哪些专用数据库",[198],{"type":192,"value":199},"Postgres 能替代哪些专用数据库？",{"type":186,"tag":201,"props":202,"children":203},"p",{},[204],{"type":192,"value":205},"传统架构中不同用途使用不同数据库：搜索用 Elasticsearch、缓存用 Redis、队列用 Kafka。但 Postgres 通过插件生态可以覆盖所有这些场景：全文搜索、JSON 存储、地理信息、消息队列等。",{"type":186,"tag":201,"props":207,"children":208},{},[209],{"type":192,"value":210},"这种\"一专多能\"的选型思路可以显著降低技术栈复杂度，特别适合中小团队。当数据库的扩展性足够好时，单一工具往往比多工具组合更具维护优势。",{"type":186,"tag":212,"props":213,"children":214},"blockquote",{},[215],{"type":186,"tag":201,"props":216,"children":217},{},[218,220],{"type":192,"value":219},"#周刊摘录 见：",{"type":186,"tag":221,"props":222,"children":224},"a",{"href":223},"/articles/weekly-385",[225],{"type":192,"value":226},"科技周刊第385期",{"title":178,"searchDepth":228,"depth":228,"links":229},2,[230],{"id":189,"depth":228,"text":189},"markdown","content:6.maps:_database:sql:postgres.md","content","6.maps/_database/sql/postgres.md","6.maps/_database/sql/postgres","md",[238,242],{"_path":239,"title":240,"description":241},"/maps/_database/nosql/redis","Redis","About Redis",{"_path":243,"title":244,"description":245},"/maps/_database/sql/sql","SQL","SQL（Structured Query Language，结构化查询语言）是一种用于管理和操作关系型数据库的编程语言。它用于执行各种数据库操作，如查询数据、插入记录、更新数据和删除记录。",1772185475878]